---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="HPAI Capital — Invest in the Future of Human Flourishing"
  description="HPAI Capital is the world's first tokenized impact angel fund. On-chain RWA tokens representing LP interests in a regulated fund backing AI, blockchain, and health ventures that advance human consciousness and abundance."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — Cinematic vault opening, immersive dark with gold glow
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden noise-overlay" style="
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%,  oklch(0.73 0.09 82 / 0.18) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 20% 80%,   oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 85% 70%,   oklch(0.73 0.09 82 / 0.07) 0%, transparent 55%),
      conic-gradient(from 200deg at 50% 0%, oklch(0.73 0.09 82 / 0.04), transparent 40%),
      oklch(0.11 0.012 255);
  ">
    <!-- Decorative gold line from top -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-px h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand-500/40 to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-28 md:py-36 text-center">

      <!-- Eyebrow -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-10 animate-fade-in">
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-500/60"></span>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-body font-500 text-brand-500">Tokenized Impact Fund</span>
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-brand-500/60"></span>
      </div>

      <!-- Main headline -->
      <h1 class="font-display font-600 text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[5.5rem] leading-[1.06] tracking-tight text-surface-950 animate-slide-up" style="font-weight:600;">
        The Angel Fund That<br/>
        <em class="text-gold-shimmer not-italic" style="font-weight:300; font-style:italic;">Backs Ventures<br/>Healing the World</em>
      </h1>

      <!-- Sub headline -->
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl font-body font-300 text-surface-900 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-200">
        Tokenized LP interests in a regulated impact fund — fractional ownership, on-chain transparency, and secondary liquidity for AI and health deals that matter.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA group -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 animate-slide-up delay-300">
        <a href="#apply" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-400 text-surface-50 font-body font-500 text-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-200 rounded-none" style="letter-spacing:0.08em;">
          REQUEST ACCESS
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#thesis" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 border border-surface-300/40 hover:border-brand-500/50 text-surface-900 hover:text-brand-500 font-body font-400 text-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-200" style="letter-spacing:0.08em;">
          READ THE THESIS
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust micro-proof -->
      <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-body font-400 text-surface-800 tracking-wide animate-fade-in delay-500">
        SEC-compliant Reg D/S offering &nbsp;·&nbsp; On-chain LP tokens &nbsp;·&nbsp; Accredited investors only
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom fade into next section -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-50 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       ORIGIN STORY — Narrative, atmospheric
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="thesis" class="relative py-24 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

      <!-- Chapter label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <span class="font-display italic text-brand-500 text-lg" style="font-weight:300;">Chapter I</span>
        <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-brand-500/20"></span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] text-surface-950 mb-10" style="font-weight:400;">
        Capital that heals —<br/><em class="text-brand-500" style="font-style:italic; font-weight:300;">not just grows.</em>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-surface-900 font-body font-300 text-lg leading-[1.8]">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We founded HPAI Capital on a single conviction: that the most transformative returns of this decade will come from the intersection of artificial intelligence, blockchain infrastructure, and human health.
          </p>
          <p>
            Yet the best deals in this space remain locked inside traditional angel networks — illiquid, opaque, and accessible only to a narrow elite. We're changing that.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="mb-6">
            By issuing on-chain RWA tokens that represent verified LP interests in a regulated co-investment vehicle, we give crypto-savvy angels and conscious capital allocators the access they've always deserved — with full transparency and real secondary liquidity.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-500 font-400 font-display italic text-xl leading-relaxed" style="font-weight:400; font-style:italic;">
            "Wealth with wisdom. Capital as a healing force."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="gold-rule max-w-5xl mx-auto" />


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THREE PILLARS — Values / Investment thesis
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="pillars" class="relative py-24 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

      <!-- Chapter label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <span class="font-display italic text-brand-500 text-lg" style="font-weight:300;">Chapter II</span>
        <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-brand-500/20"></span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.12] text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:400;">
        Three pillars.<br/>One thesis.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-lg mb-16 max-w-xl">
        Every deal we back must advance at least one pillar — and the highest-conviction opportunities advance all three.
      </p>

      <!-- Pillars grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 md:gap-px" style="background: oklch(0.73 0.09 82 / 0.12);">

        <!-- Pillar I -->
        <div class="relative glass-card p-10 md:p-12 overflow-hidden group hover:bg-surface-200/70 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 font-display text-[7rem] leading-none text-brand-500/5 select-none pointer-events-none" style="font-weight:700; font-style:italic;">I</span>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-8 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/30 rounded-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:600;">Frontier AI<br/>&amp; Blockchain</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-500 mb-4"></div>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed">
              AI systems that augment human intelligence, and blockchain infrastructure that enables trustless coordination at scale. We back teams building the rails for the next decade.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar II -->
        <div class="relative glass-card p-10 md:p-12 overflow-hidden group hover:bg-surface-200/70 transition-colors duration-300" style="background: oklch(0.20 0.025 240 / 0.7);">
          <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 font-display text-[7rem] leading-none text-teal-500/8 select-none pointer-events-none" style="font-weight:700; font-style:italic; color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.07);">II</span>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-8 flex items-center justify-center border rounded-sm" style="border-color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.35);">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172);" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:600;">Human Health<br/>&amp; Wellness</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px mb-4" style="background: oklch(0.77 0.10 172);"></div>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Longevity, mental health, preventive care, and consciousness technologies. Ventures that give people more time, clarity, and vitality — the foundation of all abundance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar III -->
        <div class="relative glass-card p-10 md:p-12 overflow-hidden group hover:bg-surface-200/70 transition-colors duration-300">
          <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 font-display text-[7rem] leading-none text-brand-500/5 select-none pointer-events-none" style="font-weight:700; font-style:italic;">III</span>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-8 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/30 rounded-sm">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:600;">Positive Media<br/>&amp; Narrative</h3>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-500 mb-4"></div>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Platforms and studios shaping the cultural stories of our time — because narrative infrastructure determines which futures we collectively build toward.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="gold-rule max-w-5xl mx-auto" />


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS — Process / Structure
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="structure" class="relative py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

      <!-- Chapter label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <span class="font-display italic text-brand-500 text-lg" style="font-weight:300;">Chapter III</span>
        <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-brand-500/20"></span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.12] text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:400;">
        How HPAI works.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-lg mb-16 max-w-xl">
        A compliant, transparent structure that brings the best of private equity and Web3 into one cohesive vehicle.
      </p>

      <!-- Steps — vertical timeline feel -->
      <div class="space-y-0">

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 md:gap-12 pb-12 relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/40 bg-surface-100/50 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="font-display text-brand-500 text-xl" style="font-weight:600;">01</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-px bg-brand-500/15 mt-4"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 pb-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">Fund Formation &amp; Compliance</h3>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              HPAI Capital operates as a Reg D / Reg S compliant SPV. Accredited investors are KYC/AML verified before receiving allocation. The fund agreement is immutably encoded on-chain, ensuring every LP can audit the terms at any time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 md:gap-12 pb-12 relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/40 bg-surface-100/50 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="font-display text-brand-500 text-xl" style="font-weight:600;">02</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-px bg-brand-500/15 mt-4"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 pb-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">AI-Assisted Deal Sourcing</h3>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Our proprietary AI pipeline screens thousands of early-stage opportunities across the three pillars, scoring each on financial viability, team quality, and programmable impact metrics. The top deals surface to our human partners for final diligence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 md:gap-12 pb-12 relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/40 bg-surface-100/50 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="font-display text-brand-500 text-xl" style="font-weight:600;">03</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-px bg-brand-500/15 mt-4"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3 pb-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">RWA Token Issuance</h3>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Each verified LP interest is represented by an on-chain RWA token. Your fractional ownership, distributions, and impact covenant data are all readable on-chain — no black box, no quarterly PDF waiting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 md:gap-12 relative">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-brand-500/40 bg-surface-100/50 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="font-display text-brand-500 text-xl" style="font-weight:600;">04</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-3">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">Liquidity &amp; Impact Reporting</h3>
            <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Secondary market trading of LP tokens is enabled through our partner DEX infrastructure — providing liquidity that traditional angel funds simply cannot offer. Quarterly impact reports track both financial returns and real-world measurable outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="gold-rule max-w-5xl mx-auto" />


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       METRICS — Dual-return language: Gold = financial, Teal = impact
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden noise-overlay" style="
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 80% 50%, oklch(0.73 0.09 82 / 0.08) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 10% 60%, oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
      oklch(0.15 0.018 245);
  ">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

      <p class="font-display italic text-brand-500 text-lg mb-12" style="font-weight:300;">By the numbers</p>

      <!-- Legend -->
      <div class="flex gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-brand-500"></div>
          <span class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm tracking-wide">Financial Return</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full" style="background: oklch(0.77 0.10 172);"></div>
          <span class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm tracking-wide">Impact Metric</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 md:gap-8">

        <div class="border-t border-brand-500/30 pt-6">
          <p class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl gold-glow text-brand-500 leading-none mb-3" style="font-weight:300;">$50M</p>
          <p class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-snug">Target fund size, first close</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t pt-6" style="border-color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.35);">
          <p class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl teal-glow leading-none mb-3" style="font-weight:300; color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172);">3×</p>
          <p class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-snug">Minimum measurable human-health outcomes per portfolio company</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-500/30 pt-6">
          <p class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl gold-glow text-brand-500 leading-none mb-3" style="font-weight:300;">$25K</p>
          <p class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-snug">Minimum LP token investment</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t pt-6" style="border-color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172 / 0.35);">
          <p class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl teal-glow leading-none mb-3" style="font-weight:300; color: oklch(0.77 0.10 172);">100%</p>
          <p class="font-body font-400 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-snug">On-chain verifiable impact covenants for every portfolio deal</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHO IT'S FOR — Target audience
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="who" class="relative py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

      <!-- Chapter label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <span class="font-display italic text-brand-500 text-lg" style="font-weight:300;">Chapter IV</span>
        <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-brand-500/20"></span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.12] text-surface-950 mb-4" style="font-weight:400;">
        Built for a new kind<br/>of investor.
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-lg mb-16 max-w-xl">
        HPAI is for those who believe capital should be a healing force — and who want the infrastructure to act on that belief.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Audience 1 -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-surface-300/20 hover:border-brand-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">Crypto-Native Angels</h3>
          <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Accredited investors with $250K–$5M in crypto net worth who want regulated, compliant exposure to early-stage AI and health deals — without abandoning the transparency of Web3.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Audience 2 -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-surface-300/20 hover:border-brand-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">Conscious Capital Allocators</h3>
          <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            ESG family offices and impact-first allocators seeking measurable positive outcomes and competitive financial returns — with programmable covenants that hold portfolio companies accountable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Audience 3 -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-surface-300/20 hover:border-brand-500/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-surface-950 mb-3" style="font-weight:600;">Web3 / DeFi Participants</h3>
          <p class="font-body font-300 text-surface-900 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            DeFi power users and DAO contributors who understand tokenization deeply and want a co-investment structure that bridges on-chain capital with off-chain venture returns.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="gold-rule max-w-5xl mx-auto" />


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       TESTIMONIAL / MANIFESTO PULL QUOTE
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="font-display italic text-brand-500/60 text-6xl leading-none">&ldquo;</span>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-surface-950 leading-[1.2] mb-10" style="font-weight:300; font-style:italic;">
        We are not building another fund.<br/>We are building a new language<br/>for what capital can mean.
      </blockquote>
